Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:05.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}不要放开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:07.39,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}不要遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:10.92,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}我一直都在等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:15.74,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}这闪闪发光的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:22.84,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}我会小心翼翼的包起来 并送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.57,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}你在那里等着
